        "heading_wFPXMM": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "<h2>A Franke Faucet; High Quality Elegance</h2>",
            "heading_size": "h1"
          }
        },
        "text_KGXbeM": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<h3>Why Choose Franke for Your Kitchen?</h3><p>Franke’s dedication to excellence has made them a go-to brand for discerning homeowners. Designed with both beauty and practicality in mind, Franke products are perfect for Australian kitchens where both aesthetics and efficiency matter. Whether you're renovating your kitchen or simply upgrading, you can count on Franke for innovative designs, sustainable solutions, and enduring quality.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
